yobservedwithfunctionalmagneticresonanceimaging.Nat. networksinchildren.PLoSBiol.7,1–5\\nRev.Neurosci.8,700–711 117 Muller-Linow,M.etal.(2008)Organizationofexcitabledynamicsin\\n90 Bressler,S.L.andKelso,J.A.(2001)Corticalcoordinationdynamics hierarchicalbiologicalnetworks.PLoSBiol.4\n\n[工具输出已截断：原始 1 行，原始 38696 字符；保留 1 行，29922 字符；截断位置：第 29922 字符附近。请不要假设后续内容已读取。]"
